Additionally, the paper mentions using neural networks for image classification, which suggests it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper's focus on understanding and improving current models suggests it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper's use of natural language processing techniques suggests it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
